How to deploy mssql

"For Linux Environment"
-----------------------

Docker:
# ------------BUILD
`docker build -t database-b-build .\mssql-with-migration`
# ------------RUN
`docker run -p 1433:1433 --name database-b -h database-b -v mssql -d --rm database-b-build`
# ------------INTERACT
`docker exec -it database-b "bash"`
# ------------SIGN INTO DATABASE
`sqlcmd -S localhost -U SA -P "d6j#Kl6pSJde7"`

